h2#jquery jQuery plugin

p.
  If you are going to use Kefir together with jQuery, you might be interested in the
  #[a(href='https://github.com/pozadi/kefir-jquery') kefir-jquery] plugin.
  It contains two handy methods #[tt $().asKefirStream] and #[tt $().asKefirProperty]
  for creating streams and properties from events of jQuery objects.





